    :Property codeCoverage
    :Access Public Instance
    ‚ćĚ If specified this must be an instance of the `CodeCoverage` class with all relevant properties set.
    ‚ćĚ This is then used to collect code coverage data. The `CodeCoverage` class also offers methods to
    ‚ćĚ aggregate the collected data and to generate an HTML report from it; see there for details.
        ‚ąá r‚Üźget
          r‚Üź_codeCoverage
        ‚ąá
        ‚ąá set value;buff;bool
          'Is not an instance of the "CodeCoverage" class'Assert‚ą®/'[CodeCoverage]'‚ć∑‚ćēvalue.NewValue
          :If 0<‚ČĘvalue.NewValue
              _codeCoverage‚Üźvalue.NewValue
          :Else
              _codeCoverage‚Üź''
          :EndIf
        ‚ąá
    :EndProperty

