        ‚ąá r‚Üźget
          r‚Üź_IniFolder
        ‚ąá
        ‚ąá set arg
          :If 0<‚ČĘarg.NewValue
              'Must be a simple character vector'Assert 1=‚Č°arg.NewValue
              'Must be a simple character vector'Assert 0‚Č†1‚ÜĎ0‚ćī‚ąäarg.NewValue
              'Must be a simple character vector'Assert 1=‚ćī‚ćīarg.NewValue
              'Does not exist'Assert 0‚Č†‚éēNEXISTS arg.NewValue
              'Is not a folder'Assert 1=1 ‚éēNINFO arg.NewValue
          :EndIf
          _IniFolder‚Üźarg.NewValue
        ‚ąá
    :EndProperty

