    ‚ąá {(rc log)}‚ÜźRun__ ps;‚éēTRAP;rc2;filename;tno;buff;res;initialFlag
        ‚ćĚ Run all test cases to be found in `_ref`.\\
        ‚ćĚ The right argument is a parameter space, typically created by calling `CreateParms ‚ć¨`.\\
        ‚ćĚ The shy explicit result is a two-element vector:
        ‚ćĚ 1. `r ‚Üź‚Üí  0 <log>`  when all tests got executed succesfully.\\
        ‚ćĚ    `r ‚Üź‚Üí  1 <log>`  when at least one test failed
        ‚ćĚ    `r ‚Üź‚Üí  2 <log>   when `Initial` prevented any test case to be executed.\\
        ‚ćĚ 2. Nested vector with the log information
