      _INI‚Üź‚ć¨                   ‚ćĚ Flatten any leftovers
      ps.(log errCounter failedCounter totalCounter)‚Üź'' 0 0 0
      ps.guiFlag‚ąß‚Üź'Win'‚Č°A.GetOperatingSystem ‚ć¨  ‚ćĚ Windows only, if at all
