    ‚ąá {success}‚ÜźExecuteInitial(ref ps);report;buff;initMsg
      success‚Üź1
      report‚Üź'Looking for a function "Initial": '
      initMsg‚Üź''
      :If 3=ref.‚éēNC'Initial'
          :If 2‚äÉ‚ĆĹ(8‚ćī2)‚ä§ps.stop
              (‚ą™(‚éēSTOP 1‚äÉ‚éēSI),‚ąÜstop_before_initial_1,‚ąÜstop_before_initial_2,‚ąÜstop_before_initial_3,‚ąÜstop_before_initial_4)‚éēSTOP 1‚äÉ‚éēSI
          :Else
