    ‚ąá {r}‚Üźref ProcessGroup ps;list;groups;grp;collect;without
    ‚ćĚ `def` is a group definition or a specific test case.
    ‚ćĚ This function
      r‚Üź‚ć¨
      ps.group‚Üźps.group[‚ćč'~'=‚äÉ¬®ps.group]    ‚ćĚ Make sure "without" is handled at the very end
      list‚ÜźRemove‚ąÜTest_¬®ps.list             ‚ćĚ All
      groups‚ÜźRemove‚ąÜTest_¬®ps.group
      collect‚Üź''
      :If 1=‚ČĘgroups
      :AndIf '~'=‚äÉ‚äÉgroups
