      :Else
          :For grp :In groups                   ‚ćĚ Loops over group definitions and collect hits
              :If '~'=1‚ćīgrp
                  :Leave
              :EndIf
              :If '*'‚ąägrp
                  collect,‚Üź(list{(‚ÜĎ‚ćļ)[;‚ć≥‚ČĘ‚ćĶ]‚ąß.=‚ćĶ}grp~'*')/list
              :ElseIf ‚ąß/grp‚ąä‚éēD                  ‚ćĚ Specific test case rather than group?
                  collect,‚Üź((‚ÜĎlist)[;‚ć≥‚ČĘgrp]‚ąß.=grp)/list
              :ElseIf '_'‚ąägrp
              :AndIf ‚ąß/({‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®‚ćĶ‚ć≥'_'}grp)‚ąä‚éēD
                  collect,‚Üź(list‚Č°¬®‚äāgrp)/list
              :Else
                  collect,‚Üź(({~'_'‚ąä‚ćĶ:'' ‚čĄ ‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®¬Į1+‚ćĶ‚ć≥'_'}¬®list)‚Č°¬®‚äāgrp)/list
              :EndIf
          :EndFor
      :EndIf
      without‚Üź{‚ćĶ/‚ć®'~'=‚äÉ¬®‚ćĶ}groups
      :If 0<‚ČĘcollect
          :For grp :In without                  ‚ćĚ Loops over "without" definitions and removes stuff
              :If '*'‚ąägrp
